<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Totemic Helm Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Kyralynn in Lake Rathetear.<BR>
<BR>
2) Collect the following and give them to Kyralynn to receive your Totemic Helm.<BR>
<BR>
- Banded Helm (must be medium size)<BR>
- 1 Ground Dufrenite<BR>
- Glacier Bear Pelt (Glacier Bear in Everfrost)<BR>
- Ogreskin Chamois (Lizard Page in Cazic Thule)</div>
<BR>
<table width=100% cellspacing=10>
