<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Taimada</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-15 03:04:24</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>wow, just killed that bear !!!!!!  get on, doesnt see him, then i went to dinner.  When i log back on 5 hrs later, use sense animal and its on track. following the heading and i found a super HUGE polar bear walking around.  Root it, send pet, and DoT with poison and disease (BTW it is not hitting very hard, DO NOT USE DD, it resists)<BR>
In my opinion, camp your character at the 3 Ice Bones house.  Use sense animal to see if it is there, if not, log off and do other thing, check back every hour or so.  Thats how i got mine, no pain at all hehe.  Just kind of scary when i first get in the cave ehhee.<BR>
